short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: It's about click. It's about you time. It's about you profile. Use it.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: By using this script, you can automate tasks such as liking posts, subscribing to pages, approving connection requests, sending connection requests, and endorsing skills. This can help you save time and perform these actions even when you don't have the time to do so manually.
